01:25.376 --> 01:29.422
She sang me the entire
<i>Mamma Mia!</i> soundtrack on my voicemail.

01:29.422 --> 01:31.007
I'll play it. It's 57 minutes.

01:31.007 --> 01:34.094
I love crazy women.
Can you give her my number?

01:34.094 --> 01:36.179
Good call on the seaport.
I get motion sickness.

01:36.179 --> 01:37.097
Whoa!

01:37.972 --> 01:38.807
It's just a teddy.

01:40.517 --> 01:41.726
We thought you were cool, Dane.

01:41.726 --> 01:44.479
