<i>♪ Here I go again ♪</i>

09:12.385 --> 09:15.179
<i>♪ My, my, how can I resist you? ♪</i>

09:15.179 --> 09:16.847
- Called it.

09:18.516 --> 09:21.435
Shoot him in the calf.
