Old Cavity-Search Constantine.

10:15.323 --> 10:16.699
Hurry up and get that body up here.

10:16.699 --> 10:19.160
I'll hide it behind the vent
near Cyrus the Cannibal's cell.

10:19.160 --> 10:21.996
