I'm not the most impressive guy.

10:51.108 --> 10:53.110
I'm a mediocre oboist

10:53.110 --> 10:55.905
who's auditioned for <i>Wheel of Fortune</i>
four times and never been picked.

10:55.905 --> 10:58.115
