10:58.115 --> 11:00.576
if maybe when we get back,

11:02.495 --> 11:03.913
you wanna go on a date with me.

11:05.581 --> 11:08.209
<i>I... thought you'd never ask.</i>

11:09.418 --> 11:12.838
<i>I'll see you when you get back.
And Barry, Pat Sajak's a dick.</i>

11:18.302 --> 11:20.137
I know you were really scared today.

11:20.137 --> 11:22.139
