the more you're gonna hurt him.

14:26.657 --> 14:27.908
It's just my opinion.

14:29.451 --> 14:30.369
But I know...

14:35.291 --> 14:36.542
it is your decision.

14:57.354 --> 14:58.856
- Oh.

15:00.941 --> 15:02.568
- Is Boro talking yet?
<i>-</i> <i>No.</i>

15:02.568 --> 15:05.321
