with why my top operative

15:05.321 --> 15:08.073
thought it was a good idea
to hire his ex at his cover job.

15:08.073 --> 15:10.451
- You know?
<i>-</i> <i>I'm a regional CIA director.</i>

15:10.451 --> 15:13.329
I know your milk's gone bad before you do.

15:13.329 --> 15:16.624
