Merry Fitness' paperwork.

15:16.624 --> 15:18.208
<i>Tally was trying to get a job,</i>

15:18.208 --> 15:20.127
and I'm trying to win her back.

15:21.045 --> 15:23.172
So, um, I know it was not a smart idea.

15:23.172 --> 15:24.465
No, it wasn't.

15:24.465 --> 15:27.092
But we may be in the clear.
Seems she's stopped digging.

15:33.015 --> 15:34.725
I'm not so sure about that.

15:34.725 --> 15:36.226
We have to talk.

15:44.360 --> 15:47.279
Before you say anything,
let me explain to you--

15:47.279 --> 15:49.031
It's Romi.

15:51.200 --> 15:52.451
She's sick.

16:00.960 --> 16:03.504
