adverse reaction to the chemo.

16:03.504 --> 16:05.673
<i>She's gonna need bone marrow
sooner than we thought.</i>

16:05.673 --> 16:07.049
I hate that I wasn't a match.

16:07.049 --> 16:09.760
- How's your donor drive idea?
<i>-</i> <i>I talked to the superintendent.</i>

16:09.760 --> 16:11.428
