16:16.892 --> 16:19.061
I know. I told him it was for my niece.

16:19.061 --> 16:21.480
<i>I begged him.
Said he had to talk to the lawyers.</i>

16:23.023 --> 16:25.442
Look, if your school district
got behind this,

16:25.442 --> 16:27.653
we could reach 10,000 people in a day.

16:27.653 --> 16:30.030
I swear to you, I am doing the best I can.

16:30.906 --> 16:33.242
Okay, look, I gotta take another call.
Just get it done.

16:33.242 --> 16:34.368
<i>I will do my best.</i>

16:34.368 --> 16:35.911
- I... I love you--

16:36.412 --> 16:37.621
H-- Hello?

16:48.215 --> 16:49.258
Hi, Kyle.

16:51.093 --> 16:51.927
