16:52.928 --> 16:54.596
- Wh... What the hell is this?
- Hi, Kyle.

16:57.850 --> 16:59.435
Oh, I get it.

16:59.977 --> 17:04.356
You're her old man,
but you can't raise the kickstand anymore,

17:04.356 --> 17:06.358
