17:41.393 --> 17:42.436
And my niece.

17:44.104 --> 17:45.647
And my grandniece.

17:47.816 --> 17:49.068
Thanks, Kyle.

17:49.068 --> 17:51.070
I'll get this to the lab.

17:54.823 --> 17:56.784
